# Copy this file to .env.local (already gitignored) and fill in the real key.
# Get a key from https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
#
# SECURITY NOTE: This is a Create React App (CRA) project. Any REACT_APP_* env
# var is baked into the production JS bundle at build time and is fully visible
# to anyone who opens browser devtools / inspects the network tab. This is only
# acceptable because this admin panel is used by trusted internal staff. If this
# panel is ever exposed to a broader audience, move Gemini calls behind a small
# backend proxy instead and remove this client-side key entirely.
REACT_APP_GEMINI_API_KEY=
